msgid ""
"Returns the sum of two Chebyshev series `c1` + `c2`.  The arguments are "
"sequences of coefficients ordered from lowest order term to highest, i.e., "
"[1,2,3] represents the series ``T_0 + 2*T_1 + 3*T_2``."
